      "title": "Economic crisis; The proposal to increase the price of rice is heating up the mill owners' media briefing",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "A heated situation arose at a media briefing held in Colombo today to raise awareness on rice prices.",
        "The heated situation arose after Newratna rice chief Mithrapala Lankeshwara said there was a need to increase the Nadu price after Temple Rice Governor Dudley Sirisena said the government would supply rice at controlled prices."
      ],
